{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/2014/09/12/Visual-Studio-安裝Node-js-Tools/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Visual Studio - 安裝Node.js Tools","date":"12 September 2014","author":"Sky Chang","excerpt":null,"tags":["Node.js","npm","Visual Studio"],"coverImage":null},"id":"9c208a22-8426-5b43-a05c-97baa0fdeb9d","html":"<p>最近因為某些需求裝了Node.js，而裝了Node.js後，又覺得不使用一下Node.js Tools for Visual Studio感覺很對不起機器上的Visual Studio…於是就誕生出了這篇…( 其實這篇也是安裝的過程中，順便紀錄的… )</p>\n<p>首先，我們要先到Node.js的官網，到這 裡<a href=\"http://nodejs.org/download/\">下載</a>，Windows版本就有分兩種，一種是msi，另外一個是exe。</p>\n<p>如果你是懶人，就選擇msi，他會幫你把環境變數等等相關資訊都弄好，或是選擇純粹的node.exe檔案，但這樣，你的PATH、npm就要自行準備與設定。</p>\n<p>這邊小弟使用msi來安裝~~</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-mhxLBRa4wnY/VBLB58YVWoI/AAAAAAAAJ38/RuRAHbhbx-k/s1600-h/image4.png\"><img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-ITyI5VcXXeQ/VBLB6sb43II/AAAAAAAAJ4E/vgSWw6jXWdo/image_thumb2.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>下載完之後，就安裝就對了…</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-kj26_httvks/VBLB7T7BCBI/AAAAAAAAJ4M/aw1V12GTfsg/s1600-h/image9.png\"><img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-0Hw-3Owdw7A/VBLB8VVNypI/AAAAAAAAJ4U/G9R8oce7-aw/image_thumb5.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>安裝完成後，要到<a href=\"http://nodejstools.codeplex.com/\">這裡</a>下載Node.js Tools for Visual Studio。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-JaXdP_OK5v0/VBLB9Mep0lI/AAAAAAAAJ4c/n2MgclyAT2A/s1600-h/image14.png\"><img src=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-9vo84pwd9ew/VBLB90WmYCI/AAAAAAAAJ4k/n2frYfMPPbk/image_thumb8.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>然後就給他安裝下去就對了= =+，接下來，就可以看到Node.js的專案範本了…</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-0w1PwamNw-I/VBLB-tcYkUI/AAAAAAAAJ4s/Ib_AzojxUrI/s1600-h/image%25255B4%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-iAGMYxCBXlE/VBLB_grYs2I/AAAAAAAAJ40/lWGwlryWdGs/image_thumb%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>完成之後，也可以透過Visual Studio去控管npm</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-Zy88IMX8J14/VBLCA-D2Y-I/AAAAAAAAJ48/38h0_L8CUyY/s1600-h/image%25255B13%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/-RaRWvDM5J9k/VBLCBvWURJI/AAAAAAAAJ5E/za8PvH3rvPE/image_thumb%25255B6%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>另外也可以透過VS工具來執行命令。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-TPLp47kKSgc/VBLCCvcyaVI/AAAAAAAAJ5M/VhI_WR3-YGE/s1600-h/image%25255B18%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-oroeJGXXhk0/VBLCDtW2ZxI/AAAAAAAAJ5U/0tLlfamBFbw/image_thumb%25255B9%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>不過前面還要加一個點，就是了…<a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-Rmmf4y24bHk/VBLCECvEphI/AAAAAAAAJ5c/Ju7VcLBIu-k/s1600-h/image%25255B23%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-KpA5TeW4TKk/VBLCFAI8j4I/AAAAAAAAJ5k/M5U8LNt_Kss/image_thumb%25255B12%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>按下執行，就會開始跑了，現在連Hello World都不用寫了XDDD</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lh3.ggpht.com/-QWbKLoEr3d0/VBLCF1WRRwI/AAAAAAAAJ5s/O-veZV9f-Pk/s1600-h/image%25255B8%25255D.png\"><img src=\"http://lh4.ggpht.com/-5amNCe1pkD8/VBLCG5GKwnI/AAAAAAAAJ50/n4961WjPAcY/image_thumb%25255B3%25255D.png?imgmax=800\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\"></a></p>\n<p>完成之後，就可以進入Node.js的開發人生了!! (疑!?)</p>\n<h4>參考資料</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.codedata.com.tw/javascript/using-nodejs-to-learn-javascript/\" title=\"http://www.codedata.com.tw/javascript/using-nodejs-to-learn-javascript/\">http://www.codedata.com.tw/javascript/using-nodejs-to-learn-javascript/</a>  <li><a href=\"http://www.infoq.com/cn/articles/nodejs-npm-install-config\" title=\"http://www.infoq.com/cn/articles/nodejs-npm-install-config\">http://www.infoq.com/cn/articles/nodejs-npm-install-config</a>  <li><a href=\"http://www.nodebeginner.org/index-zh-tw.html\" title=\"http://www.nodebeginner.org/index-zh-tw.html\">http://www.nodebeginner.org/index-zh-tw.html</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"最近因為某些需求裝了Node.js，而裝了Node.js後，又覺得不使用一下Node.js Tools for Visual Studio感覺很對不起機器上的Visual Studio…於是就誕生出了這篇…( 其實這篇也是安裝的過程中，順便紀錄的… ) 首先，我們要先到Node…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Azure - 實作Azure上的AD與MVC進行驗證 - Azure設定篇 ( 三 )","tags":["Active Directory","ASP.NET MVC","Azure"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2014/09/03/Azure-實作Azure上的AD與MVC進行驗證-Azure設定篇-三/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/blog.sanc.idv.tw/Azure-實作Azure上的AD與MVC進行驗證-Azure設定篇-三.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"npm -  為什麼在Windows底下更新npm無效","tags":["Node.js","npm"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2014/09/13/npm-為什麼在Windows底下更新npm無效/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/blog.sanc.idv.tw/npm-為什麼在Windows底下更新npm無效.md"}}}}